log:
AT updates for The Lost City of Un’Goro.

After readapting your deck in Underground Arena, AT will detect the removed cards — outlined in white in your deck tab — and remove them from your deck automatically.

Premium: When redrafting after a loss in Underground Arena, AT will display card scores in the deck tab for each card currently in your deck. It will also highlight the 5 weakest cards (per draft assistant HA/HSR), so you know which ones are the weakest links.

Premium: Leaderboard searches are working again for the new underground arena.

More details on the github
